text: "The Entertainer" is a 1974 song by Billy Joel and is the only single from his third studio album Streetlife Serenade. It went to number 30 in Canada, number 34 in the United States and number 89 in Australia. ==References== Category:1974 songs Category:Billy Joel songs Category:Waylon Jennings songs Category:Folk rock songs Category:Pop rock songs
